title: 698. Skill Positions Draft
itunes:title: 698. Skill Positions Draft
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. On this special show, the guys do a skill positions only draft where they each draft 3 tight ends, 5 running backs, 5 wide receivers and 5 quarterbacks.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
